txt.en: 'Well met again, [placeholder]. The Khâlbina is one of our finest merchant ships. She is sailing to Jax Phanâl on the morrow. There are rumours of huge beasts, giant crabs, and who knows what else, clamouring aboard ships near Jax Phanâl. These are simple merchant vessels, and their crews are not used to defending themselves from such beasts. Would you protect the Khâlbina and her crew on this perilous journey?'
You have successfully defeated the crabs and protected the Khâlbina! Return with the Umbari scout to the mission giver with this report.
There is no twist in this mission.
Protect the Khâlbina and her crew from dangers while sailing to Jax Phanâl on the Cape of Umbar.
'Well that is quite the tale. I am so glad you were there to take on those dreadful beasts and ensure the crew's safety. Thank you for your valiant deeds.'
'Your objective is clear, [placeholder], protect the Khâlbina at all cost. The hopes of the Khâlbina and her crew rest upon your able shoulders.'
Complete Mission: An Infestation of Crabs
Your mission is to protect the merchant ship Khâlbina on its trip to Jax Phanâl.\n\nSpeak to Deshra to travel.
